data.name: lblexplain.Text
data.value: Nii-San, I lost my cats! Could you help me gather them all up again? Just use the ASDW keys to move around and catch them. I'm really sad, so could you get them all for me in 60 seconds? There should be twenty, but if you catch more that's awesome! Oh yeah, be sure to stay away from Black Hayate, you know dogs scare cats! If you catch him I'll bet at least 3 cats will run away from you! Please help, Nii-san!
